- `src/StarterGui/Effects/LayerEnterBanner.lua (5종 톤 확장)`
- `src/StarterGui/Elevator/ElevatorPanel.lua`
- `src/StarterGui/HUD/ReturnToSurfaceButton.lua`
- `src/server/ServerMain.server.lua (Phase 04 mount)`
- `src/client/ClientMain.client.lua (Phase 04 mount)`
- `tests/p04.lua`

